review: It was a good experience. We had some questions when we asked her to answer it. I have already recommended the doctor to others, she does give time for the consultation. We are happy to visit her for the consultation we wanted to know about the personal issue. It was just 5-10min of short consultation happy with that.

*** ********* *** ***** Doctor behaviour was good and she listened to our problem very well. I took gynaecologist related treatment and I am satisfied with doctor treatment. I would like to recommend this doctor to others and I will give a rating of 8/10. When it comes to improvement, sometimes there is waiting time for scanning, otherwise, everything is good.

When I book it was  Dr sridevi but I didn't meet her, instead of her they gave me appointment of Dr Bhargavi Reddy. Doctor was good as she explained everything nicely. She gave me to do  urine culture test and gave tablets.  Let's see that this medicine have good affect on my health. Hospital was neat and clean. It took me  more than 60 minutes. I reached there by 5.20 p.m but my appointment with the doctor was at 7.20 p.m where in practo it was at 6.00p.m

tags: Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I had visited the doctor once. She had just prescribed medicines without explaining the problem. It was a quick sit up for which they had charged me 150. Also there was a long waiting line despite making online bookings and showing up way before time. 
After this they had asked me to revisit, just to said ok good. That's all. For which I had to repay the fee.
I took my wife for the consultation. The doctor name showed in Practo is Dr.Sridevi, but in the hospital we were asked to consult with Dr.Bhargavi Reddy.  ************ *** **** **** *** *******
